            <title>[LU-7932] Patch e2fsprogs to allow set special flag to FS increase a hash tree levels</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7932</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Two level hash tree and leaf block which consist up 300 directory entry&lt;br/&gt;
Total number of directory entry limited by ~20 millions entries&lt;br/&gt;
Hash collisions decrease real directory size &lt;br/&gt;
Solution: increase a hash tree levels, patch e2fsprogs and allow set special flag to FS.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
